5:
What was that?! Somethin's at the 
World Flipper!
9:
Relax, it's just Lilial, up to her usual 
experiments.
18:
Aw, man, I totally thought I had it this 
time.
23: Grrr, I'm all out of ideas!
26:
Hey! The hell happened over there? 
*sniff* Something smells burnt.
31:
"Alchemy" happened.
*sigh* I don't know what she's trying 
to make, but all her experiments end 
in explosions.
35:
What, you mean she blew something 
up?!
37:
She nearly blew my eardrums out! 
So much for my afternoon catnap…
43:
Oh, c'mon, that was just a little one! 
Imagine how boring alchemy would 
be without explosions—they're what 
keep the long experiments fun!
45:
Also, I've got competition. There are 
rumors in Palpebra of an alchemist 
who blows up everything they touch—
and I'm not gonna sit by and let them 
take my throne!
48:
You're competing to see which of you 
sucks at alchemy more?
51:
Just don't go TOO crazy, okay? I dunno
what you're working on, but it doesn't 
seem to be going well.
59:
The theory all looks good on paper, 
but nothing's working in practice. 
Argh, I just KNOW I'm overthinking 
something, but I don't know WHAT!
63:
So you're just blowing random stuff up
hoping it'll work? You're joking, right?
65:
What if you accidentally blow yourself
up?
70:
If I... Wait, that's it! You're a genius, 
Nimbus!
80:
I'm gonna go blow random stuff up 
until something works! All this time, 
I was too worried I'd get caught up in 
the explosion, and was holding back!
105: Ahahaaa! That was a good one!
110:
Stop, stop, STOP! No more experiments
for today! You'll hurt yourself!
113:
Hmph. She looks like she's having a 
blast.
119:
That was the biggest explosion I've 
made yet! If I'm getting different 
results than before, that means I 
made it a step in the right direction!
121:
I thought too hard about what to use 
and whether it'd blow up in my face 
that I unconsciously held myself back
—and gave up on ideas without 
trying!
124:
Go big or go home, right? No more 
ruling out possibilities 'till I've chucked 
'em in a cauldron and tried it!
126:
This breakthrough's all thank to you, 
Nimbus! Now, I've got alchemy to get 
back to! Later!
